*   [Cold War](/Cold_War)
*   [Korean War](/Korean_War)
*   [Vietnam War](/Vietnam_War)
*   [Contemporary Historical Examination of Current Operations](/Contemporary_Historical_Examination_of_Current_Operations) (CHECO)
