*   [Operation Just Cause](/United_States_invasion_of_Panama) (1989–1990 U.S. invasion of Panama)
*   [Gulf War](/Gulf_War) (1990–1991)
    *   Operation Desert Shield (1990–1991)
    *   Operation Desert Storm (1991)
