*   [Operation Allied Force](/Operation_Allied_Force) (1999 NATO bombing of Yugoslavia)
*   [Afghanistan War](/Afghanistan_War) (2001–2021)
    *   [Operation Enduring Freedom](/Operation_Enduring_Freedom) (2001–2014)
