#### U – Utility

Utility aircraft are employed for various purposes as needed. For example, a [Huey](/Bell_Huey_family) helicopter might be used for personnel transport around a large base or launch site, or for evacuation missions. These aircraft are versatile and generally used for troop and cargo transport.

