The [VC-25A](/Boeing_VC-25) ([Air Force One](/Air_Force_One)) flying over [Mount Rushmore](/Mount_Rushmore) in 2001. These aircraft are dedicated to the transportation of Very Important Persons (VIPs), including the President, Vice President, cabinet secretaries, government officials, the Joint Chiefs of Staff, and other key personnel.

